                            h2 Technologies
                            p  theFlow is being developing with use of up-to-date technologies. We use Spring, Spring Security, Hibernate, MySql, Thymeleaf, Grunt, Bower. Now you can see the short version of the project. Many modules and features are going to be added, or are in work just now, such as time management and agile tools.
